definitions.definition: ( US , Pennsylvania , Mid-Atlantic US ) A sandwich made on a (usually soft) long Italian roll; a submarine sandwich .
examples: I'm going to Wawa to get a hoagie for lunch.

main_definition: ( US , Pennsylvania , Mid-Atlantic US ) A sandwich made on a (usually soft) long Italian roll; a submarine sandwich .

definitions.definition: A tortilla or chapati wrap filled with meat (usually doner kebab meat; seasoned lamb or mutton ), chips and cheese.

main_definition: ( Scotland , chiefly Central Belt ) A tortilla or chapati wrap filled with meat (usually doner kebab meat; seasoned lamb or mutton ), chips and cheese.
